nodes.text: A rebel cell of the Alliance to Restore the Republic was active during the Imperial Era on the Galactic Empire capital planet of Coruscant. Its members included Quartermaster and squad leader Ko-Tun Feralo, Jarrod Kelvin and his droid J4X-7, as well as the Wookiee Drokkatta. On at least one occassion, they were assisted by Jyn Odan, a smuggler who worked for the Rebel Alliance.
